"Your talks are melodious."

764
00:56:15,798 --> 00:56:18,229
"It entices me, beloved."

765
00:56:22,191 --> 00:56:24,835
"Your complexion is lovely."

766
00:56:25,415 --> 00:56:27,970
"You're unique."

767
00:56:28,058 --> 00:56:32,818
"Seeing you I felt something."

768
00:57:05,030 --> 00:57:11,181
"You touched my body and it
kindled passion in my heart."

769
00:57:11,235 --> 00:57:17,464
"My heart skipped a beat
when your veil swayed."

770
00:57:23,548 --> 00:57:29,850
"You touched my body and it
kindled passion in my heart."

771
00:57:29,891 --> 00:57:35,969
"My heart skipped a beat
when your veil swayed."

772
00:57:36,010 --> 00:57:39,086
"I'll fill my life with your love."

773
00:57:39,140 --> 00:57:42,211
"I've given you my life."

774
00:57:42,312 --> 00:57:45,459
"I'll come to your house as your bride."

775
00:57:45,492 --> 00:57:48,332
"I crave for you."

776
00:57:48,489 --> 00:57:51,242
"I can't explain my restlessness to you."

777
00:57:51,271 --> 00:57:53,566
"Your voice is sweet like a cuckoo."

778
00:57:57,404 --> 00:58:00,016
"Your face is so innocent."

779
00:58:04,022 --> 00:58:06,648
"Your eyes are lined with eyeliner."

780
00:58:07,080 --> 00:58:09,640
"Your lips are salacious."

781
00:58:09,686 --> 00:58:14,689
"Seeing you, I lost my heart."

782
00:58:20,744 --> 00:58:22,084
[THUNDER RAIN]

783
00:58:22,125 --> 00:58:22,781
Listen!

784
00:58:24,596 --> 00:58:25,716
- Listen!
- Yes!

785
00:58:26,384 --> 00:58:27,477
Where were you lost?

786
00:58:30,528 --> 00:58:32,308
[THUNDER RAIN]

787
00:58:32,380 --> 00:58:33,460
Thinking about somebody!

788
00:58:34,399 --> 00:58:36,759
Tell me who you were thinking about.

789
00:58:38,848 --> 00:58:40,665
- Do you want to know?
- Yes!

790
00:58:41,769 --> 00:58:42,752
Come with me!

791
00:58:51,718 --> 00:58:52,513
It's you!

792
00:58:59,732 --> 00:59:02,985
Did I make a mistake?

793
00:59:03,170 --> 00:59:06,453
Yes! You've made a grave mistake, Raju!

794
00:59:07,454 --> 00:59:08,563
A grave mistake!

795
00:59:08,634 --> 00:59:10,374
So consider this as a mistake, Saraswati!

796
00:59:10,822 --> 00:59:13,866
I love you. I truly love you.

797
00:59:14,152 --> 00:59:17,906
For God's sake, keep quiet!
It's a sin for me to hear all this!

798
00:59:18,248 --> 00:59:20,227
I'm going to marry somebody else.

799
00:59:20,506 --> 00:59:21,679
I'm engaged.

800
00:59:46,339 --> 00:59:47,167
Saraswati!

801
00:59:48,519 --> 00:59:50,820
I've hurt you unknowingly.

802
00:59:51,970 --> 00:59:53,048
Forgive me.

803
00:59:55,063 --> 00:59:57,142
Come. I'll escort you home.

804
01:00:00,715 --> 01:00:03,437
[WIND HOWLING]

805
01:00:07,337 --> 01:00:08,692
Look! They've come!

806
01:00:10,290 --> 01:00:12,374
I had told you! I don't believe this!

807
01:00:12,431 --> 01:00:14,148
Yes! If you say...

808
01:00:14,188 --> 01:00:15,495
Look there!

809
01:00:44,869 --> 01:00:47,300
[WIND HOWLING]

810
01:00:55,275 --> 01:00:58,142
Mr. Diwan,
ask your to-be daughter-in-law...

811
01:00:58,648 --> 01:01:01,096
...where she was the whole
night and what was she doing!

812
01:01:01,501 --> 01:01:04,686
Mr. Shyamlal, you only ask your daughter!

813
01:01:11,465 --> 01:01:14,534
Where were you the whole night? Answer me!

814
01:01:15,490 --> 01:01:17,479
What were you doing with this scoundrel?

815
01:01:18,546 --> 01:01:23,014
Father, you too are misunderstanding me!

816
01:01:23,306 --> 01:01:25,797
If a young daughter doesn't
return home the whole night...

817
01:01:26,618 --> 01:01:28,223
...what will her old father think?

818
01:01:29,064 --> 01:01:31,008
What will he explain to the people?

819
01:01:31,900 --> 01:01:34,355
I wish I were dead before seeing all this.

820
01:01:34,494 --> 01:01:36,745
Uncle, this isn't so!

821
01:01:37,327 --> 01:01:39,323
Actually we got stuck in a storm at night!

822
01:01:39,486 --> 01:01:41,282
Which storm are you talking about?

823
01:01:42,567 --> 01:01:46,297
The storm of lust which
had engulfed you both?

824
01:01:46,960 --> 01:01:51,376
Or the storm where without
caring for anything...

825
01:01:51,826 --> 01:01:54,066
...an unmarried girl
forsakes her coyness...

826
01:01:54,124 --> 01:01:56,581
...and she becomes naked in front
of an unknown man? -This is a lie!

827
01:01:56,628 --> 01:01:59,028
If this is a lie,
were you worshipping her the whole night?

828
01:02:01,446 --> 01:02:05,586
Along with herself,
she has slandered the entire village!

829
01:02:05,695 --> 01:02:08,562
Now who will marry the
women of our village?

830
01:02:08,642 --> 01:02:10,626
Who will form a bond with the villagers?

831
01:02:10,720 --> 01:02:13,393
Her fiance will break the bond!

832
01:02:13,432 --> 01:02:16,070
You're right! I break this alliance!

833
01:02:16,972 --> 01:02:19,628
I won't make such a characterless...

834
01:02:19,653 --> 01:02:21,439
...and derogatory woman
my daughter-in-law!

835
01:02:21,535 --> 01:02:22,615
Let's go, son!

836
01:02:22,781 --> 01:02:24,768
Stop! Listen to me!

837
01:02:25,188 --> 01:02:28,116
They're falsely accusing her!

838
01:02:28,854 --> 01:02:32,294
I swear on God!
She's chaste like holy Ganges!

839
01:02:32,764 --> 01:02:35,175
We've not committed any sin!

840
01:02:35,822 --> 01:02:38,784
Don't break this alliance!

841
01:02:38,819 --> 01:02:42,530
Forget making her my wife!
I won't even make her my mistress!

842
01:02:44,071 --> 01:02:45,983
Had you not been her to-be husband...

843
01:02:46,453 --> 01:02:49,026
...I would've retaliated!

844
01:02:50,593 --> 01:02:52,886
What did you say? You would've retaliated?

845
01:02:53,294 --> 01:02:55,574
You commit a crime! And you act smugly!

846
01:02:55,830 --> 01:02:56,843
Move!

847
01:02:58,894 --> 01:03:00,334
Villagers, what are you all looking at?

848
01:03:00,893 --> 01:03:03,934
Teach him a lesson for sleeping
with the women of our village!

849
01:03:04,194 --> 01:03:05,191
Beat him!

850
01:04:01,536 --> 01:04:02,494
Stop!

851
01:04:03,743 --> 01:04:04,854
I say stop!

852
01:04:05,764 --> 01:04:08,665
If anybody touched him, I'll hit that man!

853
01:04:09,045 --> 01:04:11,917
Whom are you threatening? Beat him!

854
01:04:14,900 --> 01:04:19,358
Bhairav, if you have guts, beat him!

855
01:04:20,165 --> 01:04:22,806
Hariya! If you have guts, beat him!

856
01:04:23,236 --> 01:04:25,975
Beat him! Come on!

857
01:04:26,251 --> 01:04:28,493
Come on, beat him!

858
01:04:29,402 --> 01:04:32,524
You are brutally beating an unarmed man!

859
01:04:33,355 --> 01:04:34,989
What do you all think?

860
01:04:35,410 --> 01:04:39,382
He's a coward! Or he can't fight back!

861
01:04:40,306 --> 01:04:43,333
He can kill you all in one blow!

862
01:04:43,837 --> 01:04:46,946
But he's quiet only because
he wants to give me justice!

863
01:04:47,158 --> 01:04:47,947
Got it?

864
01:04:48,864 --> 01:04:52,618
And you! You're worried about me!

865
01:04:53,381 --> 01:04:55,541
Yesterday you had come
to rape me at the fair!

866
01:04:56,399 --> 01:05:00,719
If yesterday this man had not been
there, you would've raped me!

867
01:05:03,284 --> 01:05:06,563
And you? You were my to-be husband!

868
01:05:07,470 --> 01:05:09,335
You wanted to marry me!

869
01:05:10,514 --> 01:05:11,884
But I think you don't know...

870
01:05:12,314 --> 01:05:14,556
...the foundation of a husband
and wife's relationship!

871
01:05:15,019 --> 01:05:16,845
It's trust!

872
01:05:17,251 --> 01:05:20,445
The man who can't trust
his wife for one night...

873
01:05:20,477 --> 01:05:22,194
...can't stand by her all her life.

874
01:05:23,275 --> 01:05:27,317
Just now you said you won't
even make me your mistress!

875
01:05:28,047 --> 01:05:30,307
Then today I say in front of everybody...

876
01:05:30,797 --> 01:05:34,188
...forget being my husband,
you can't even be a pimp!

877
01:05:35,224 --> 01:05:37,212
Here are your bangles! And get lost!

878
01:05:51,462 --> 01:05:55,443
Father, for me you're my
mother and you're my father.

879
01:05:56,309 --> 01:06:00,246
You've raised me.
You've imbibed values within me.

880
01:06:01,560 --> 01:06:03,653
Your daughter can die.

881
01:06:04,249 --> 01:06:06,333
But she can't do such a derogatory deed...

882
01:06:06,664 --> 01:06:09,319
...for which you have to feel ashamed!

883
01:06:10,621 --> 01:06:12,169
I won't let you feel ashamed, Father!

884
01:06:12,893 --> 01:06:15,973
Your Saraswati won't let you feel
ashamed in front of the world!

885
01:06:16,564 --> 01:06:17,733
She won't!

886
01:06:25,795 --> 01:06:28,967
[TEMPLE BELL]

887
01:07:23,168 --> 01:07:24,239
Will you marry me?

888
01:08:10,609 --> 01:08:12,359
- Greetings, brother!
- Greetings!

889
01:08:12,554 --> 01:08:14,994
Dear, what are you looking at?
Seek her blessings.

890
01:08:15,219 --> 01:08:17,285
- You're lucky!
- God bless you, dear.

891
01:08:17,310 --> 01:08:20,687
By fixing Raju's marriage
with my illiterate daughter...

892
01:08:20,712 --> 01:08:22,312
...you've done me a big favour!

893
01:08:22,733 --> 01:08:26,655
My daughter will live here like
a maid and not a daughter-in-law.

894
01:08:26,680 --> 01:08:30,311
Then finalise the marriage
date on the full moon night!

895
01:08:30,640 --> 01:08:32,493
As you say! [CAR ENGINE STARTS]

896
01:08:34,562 --> 01:08:35,351
Greetings!

897
01:08:36,665 --> 01:08:39,159
I don't understand, sister!

898
01:08:39,217 --> 01:08:41,597
Why did you fix Raju's
alliance with this pauper?

899
01:08:41,897 --> 01:08:43,326
If you had found a rich family...

900
01:08:43,366 --> 01:08:45,796
...you could have asked for
as much dowry as you wanted!

901
01:08:45,827 --> 01:08:47,451
Don't be foolish, brother!

902
01:08:47,801 --> 01:08:49,863
Don't you remember Raju's mother's will?

903
01:08:50,109 --> 01:08:51,595
In this, it's clearly written that...

904
01:08:51,651 --> 01:08:54,988
...Raju can't give this
wealth to anybody...

905
01:08:55,113 --> 01:08:57,093
...until his wife
doesn't give her consent!

906
01:08:57,118 --> 01:08:58,430
I understood, sister!

907
01:08:58,455 --> 01:09:00,265
You've found an illiterate
daughter-in-law...

908
01:09:00,322 --> 01:09:02,546
...so that like Raju, you can make
her give us her thumb impression...

909
01:09:02,571 --> 01:09:04,206
...and get all the wealth!

910
01:09:04,258 --> 01:09:05,367
Wow, sister!

911
01:09:05,392 --> 01:09:06,343
[LAUGHING]

912
01:09:08,905 --> 01:09:10,002
[BIRD CHIRPING]

913
01:09:10,129 --> 01:09:12,499
- Ma'am! Brother Raju has come!
- Is that so?

914
01:09:14,012 --> 01:09:14,703
Raju!

915
01:09:16,285 --> 01:09:17,548
- Raju!
- Yes, Mother!

916
01:09:17,636 --> 01:09:20,820
Where were you the last night?
I was so worried for you!

917
01:09:20,845 --> 01:09:22,157
Mother, I was stuck in a storm!

918
01:09:22,515 --> 01:09:24,221
Let it be!

919
01:09:24,875 --> 01:09:25,812
Sit!

920
01:09:26,008 --> 01:09:30,812
Today I'll give you great news!
You'll be delighted!

921
01:09:31,094 --> 01:09:33,687
Mother, I too want to give you good news!

922
01:09:33,797 --> 01:09:34,957
What good news?

923
01:09:36,061 --> 01:09:36,836
Saraswati!

924
01:09:52,054 --> 01:09:53,682
Saraswati, she's my mother.

925
01:09:57,956 --> 01:09:58,829
She...

926
01:09:58,870 --> 01:10:01,569
She's your daughter-in-law, Mother.

927
01:10:17,698 --> 01:10:22,338
The situation was such
that we had to get married.

928
01:10:33,404 --> 01:10:35,240
Won't you take your mother's blessing?

929
01:10:40,974 --> 01:10:42,711
- Mother!
- God bless you!

930
01:10:43,230 --> 01:10:45,197
Mother, are you happy with this marriage?

931
01:10:45,750 --> 01:10:48,538
How can a mother not be
happy to see her son married?

932
01:10:49,326 --> 01:10:51,322
My happiness lies in your happiness!

933
01:10:51,358 --> 01:10:54,111
Really, Mother! Did you see?
My mother is so nice!

934
01:10:54,230 --> 01:10:55,975
I had told you she won't be angry with us!

935
01:10:56,518 --> 01:11:01,002
If you're happy,
I don't want anything else!

936
01:11:06,990 --> 01:11:09,854
Sister! We're ruined!

937
01:11:09,890 --> 01:11:11,399
Our dreams are shattered!

938
01:11:11,480 --> 01:11:13,718
The way you're supporting that girl...

939
01:11:13,743 --> 01:11:17,988
...I feel very soon we'll have to
pack our bags for a pilgrimage.

940
01:11:18,037 --> 01:11:19,618
Do something, sister!

941
01:11:21,389 --> 01:11:23,389
She went without saying anything!

942
01:11:23,935 --> 01:11:28,172
In Mahabharat's 33rd episode
Shakuni too had smiled like this.

943
01:11:28,197 --> 01:11:31,277
But in the 34th episode
Draupadi was disrobed!

944
01:11:31,429 --> 01:11:35,010
Don't worry, Mainawati!
Sister will surely think of a ruse!

945
01:11:38,646 --> 01:11:40,572
My daughter-in-law is really gorgeous!

946
01:11:41,862 --> 01:11:43,742
I'm proud of Raju's choice!

947
01:11:44,928 --> 01:11:46,111
Even if I had wanted...

948
01:11:46,456 --> 01:11:50,503
...I couldn't have found such a
pretty and cultured girl for my son!

949
01:11:50,925 --> 01:11:51,744
Daughter-in-law, sit!

950
01:11:56,421 --> 01:11:57,273
Daughter-in-law, take this!

951
01:11:59,640 --> 01:12:02,102
I had made this bangle for Raju's wife!

952
01:12:03,253 --> 01:12:06,197
Let me give it to you!

953
01:12:06,889 --> 01:12:09,986
What's the matter, Mother? You're crying!

954
01:12:15,735 --> 01:12:19,561
At times God gives joy and
sorrow at the same time!

955
01:12:20,345 --> 01:12:22,647
I don't understand!

956
01:12:22,965 --> 01:12:24,367
How do I explain it to you?!

957
01:12:25,118 --> 01:12:29,549
Because what I'm going to say
is about Raju's life and death!

958
01:12:30,760 --> 01:12:32,012
What are you saying?

959
01:12:32,565 --> 01:12:35,233
I had kept it a secret.

960
01:12:36,013 --> 01:12:38,163
Today unwillingly I have to tell you that.

961
01:12:38,950 --> 01:12:41,046
Look! This is Raju's horoscope.

962
01:12:41,478 --> 01:12:44,085
- Do you know what is written in this?
- What?

963
01:12:44,351 --> 01:12:49,249
It's written that if Raju
marries before he turns 25...

964
01:12:49,558 --> 01:12:51,312
...and if his wife conceives...

965
01:12:51,915 --> 01:12:56,041
...the child could be a
danger to his father's life!

966
01:12:56,851 --> 01:12:59,256
That's why I didn't get Raju married.

967
01:12:59,678 --> 01:13:02,948
Because there is still a few
days left for him to turn 25!

968
01:13:04,253 --> 01:13:06,705
Mother, you too...

969
01:13:06,971 --> 01:13:09,330
I knew you'd say this!

970
01:13:09,647 --> 01:13:12,713
You don't believe in such orthodox things!

971
01:13:13,645 --> 01:13:15,896
But what do I do?

972
01:13:16,622 --> 01:13:18,034
I'm a mother.

973
01:13:18,662 --> 01:13:23,601
And as his mother, I beg for Raju's life!

974
01:13:24,238 --> 01:13:27,525
Daughter-in-law, for God's sake,
don't let this terrible thing happen!

975
01:13:27,871 --> 01:13:29,289
Don't let it happen!

976
01:13:29,692 --> 01:13:30,354
Mother!

977
01:13:32,157 --> 01:13:36,283
Daughter-in-law, it's just for a few days!
Listen to me!

978
01:13:36,767 --> 01:13:39,617
- I beg you!
- What are you doing?

979
01:13:42,839 --> 01:13:47,338
Fine! I'll do as you say!

980
01:13:49,061 --> 01:13:51,057
God bless you, dear!

981
01:13:51,640 --> 01:13:55,744
Look, daughter-in-law!
My Raju should never come to know!

982
01:14:22,130 --> 01:14:27,170
Saru, your love has given me a new life.

983
01:14:28,709 --> 01:14:33,269
We'll begin the first night of
our lives amidst these lamps.

984
01:14:35,528 --> 01:14:37,814
It'll fill your life with happiness.

985
01:14:39,749 --> 01:14:41,909
Saru, I've not left
any place for darkness.

986
01:14:44,103 --> 01:14:45,298
No place at all!

987
01:14:58,319 --> 01:14:59,104
No, Raju!

988
01:15:00,251 --> 01:15:01,052
Why not?

989
01:15:02,036 --> 01:15:03,543
Because I'm saying no.

990
01:15:03,982 --> 01:15:05,938
Today your Raju won't hear your refusal!

991
01:15:07,399 --> 01:15:08,599
Come close to me!

992
01:15:20,705 --> 01:15:22,330
I'm saying no, but you won't listen.

993
01:15:23,070 --> 01:15:25,329
Stay away from me! Don't touch me!

994
01:15:25,657 --> 01:15:29,236
What are you saying, Saru?
Did I make any mistake?

995
01:15:29,953 --> 01:15:32,543
Have I made any mistake? Tell me, Saru!

996
01:15:32,936 --> 01:15:35,395
Raju, please leave me alone!

997
01:15:37,601 --> 01:15:40,337
Leave you alone! That too today!

998
01:15:41,049 --> 01:15:42,100
Why, Saru?

999
01:15:42,125 --> 01:15:43,786
I don't have any answer!

1000
01:15:44,674 --> 01:15:47,080
If you don't want to go, I'll go!

1001
01:15:47,129 --> 01:15:50,806
No, Saru!
You don't have to leave this room!

1002
01:15:51,631 --> 01:15:52,674
I'll leave!

1003
01:15:54,208 --> 01:15:56,015
I don't know what lies in your heart...

1004
01:15:57,273 --> 01:15:58,993
...and for what you're punishing me.

1005
01:16:00,361 --> 01:16:01,721
But I assure you...

1006
01:16:03,016 --> 01:16:06,725
...I'll never come to you to
assert my right as a husband!

1007
01:16:07,590 --> 01:16:08,572
I'll never come, Saru!

1008
01:16:22,880 --> 01:16:24,160
Sister, wow!

1009
01:16:24,217 --> 01:16:26,657
Even Totaram bows to you!

1010
01:16:26,740 --> 01:16:29,820
You've played such a nice ruse!
Like a politician.

1011
01:16:29,877 --> 01:16:31,959
You should've been in parliament.

1012
01:16:32,002 --> 01:16:33,017
[LAUGHS]

1013
01:16:33,064 --> 01:16:37,517
By lying about Raju's life,
you've trapped her in such a way...

1014
01:16:37,542 --> 01:16:41,339
...that on your word she herself
ruined her nuptial night!

1015
01:16:41,565 --> 01:16:43,492
Now go on adding fuel to the fire.

1016
01:16:43,560 --> 01:16:47,119
And think of an idea to make this
girl leave this house in four days.

1017
01:16:47,687 --> 01:16:51,228
Our work is done! Now let's go to sleep!

1018
01:17:09,241 --> 01:17:11,815
Wow! What a great mother-in-law you are!

1019
01:17:13,219 --> 01:17:15,671
Your daughter-in-law just
stepped in this house...

1020
01:17:16,481 --> 01:17:18,673
...and you've started
showing your true colours!

1021
01:17:20,162 --> 01:17:22,001
But remember one thing!

1022
01:17:22,932 --> 01:17:26,604
You can add as much fuel as you want!

1023
01:17:27,803 --> 01:17:30,228
If I didn't teach you all a lesson...

1024
01:17:30,764 --> 01:17:32,861
...I'm not my father's daughter!

1025
01:17:33,302 --> 01:17:35,387
What's the matter?
Today you're being so romantic!

1026
01:17:35,872 --> 01:17:38,561
The weather is for romance today.

1027
01:17:39,610 --> 01:17:41,690
What are you doing? Are you fine?

1028
01:17:41,907 --> 01:17:43,625
Mainu, I'm fine!

1029
01:17:44,152 --> 01:17:48,227
But I want a flower to
blossom in our courtyard.

1030
01:17:48,617 --> 01:17:50,965
There are so many flowers here!
How many more do you want?

1031
01:17:51,038 --> 01:17:53,010
- I'm not talking about these flowers!
- So?

1032
01:17:53,109 --> 01:17:57,797
I'm talking about the child
which you'll conceive!

1033
01:17:59,290 --> 01:18:01,172
You couldn't do anything in your youth!

1034
01:18:01,437 --> 01:18:03,009
Now what will you do at this age?

1035
01:18:04,586 --> 01:18:06,398
What? You're always laughing!

1036
01:18:06,883 --> 01:18:09,000
I had gone to the market
to buy vegetables.

1037
01:18:09,048 --> 01:18:11,008
- Go and cook lunch for me!
- Fine!

1038
01:18:12,070 --> 01:18:13,922
- Mainawati, give it to me!
- Here!

1039
01:18:15,919 --> 01:18:17,906
You had asked me to bring the vegetables.

1040
01:18:18,139 --> 01:18:20,626
Gourd, cauliflower...

1041
01:18:21,821 --> 01:18:23,828
I'm talking to you. Are you listening?

1042
01:18:23,853 --> 01:18:25,699
Yes. Say whatever you'd like!

1043
01:18:26,768 --> 01:18:30,360
My Pandu, you're looking so sad today.

1044
01:18:30,385 --> 01:18:31,462
What else do you want me to be?

1045
01:18:32,929 --> 01:18:36,081
Do you know yesterday was
brother Raju's wedding night?

1046
01:18:36,575 --> 01:18:39,016
Yet he was sleeping at
the back of the house.

1047
01:18:39,911 --> 01:18:41,876
- What are you saying?
- I'm telling the truth.

1048
01:18:44,651 --> 01:18:46,341
Brother Raju's is very unfortunate.

1049
01:18:47,473 --> 01:18:49,005
His mother turned out to be a witch.

1050
01:18:49,679 --> 01:18:51,719
And the wife, exactly the same.

1051
01:18:53,373 --> 01:18:55,074
Here comes the madam.

1052
01:18:59,954 --> 01:19:01,702
Pandu, what are you making?

1053
01:19:01,860 --> 01:19:04,110
Can't you see? I'm making gourd vegetable!

1054
01:19:05,664 --> 01:19:06,784
I'll make it.

1055
01:19:07,685 --> 01:19:08,701
Here, make it!

1056
01:19:11,017 --> 01:19:12,537
Why are you talking to me like that?

1057
01:19:12,578 --> 01:19:14,662
I don't respect a woman who...

1058
01:19:14,773 --> 01:19:16,498
...doesn't have any
respect for her husband.

1059
01:19:17,189 --> 01:19:19,083
- But what have I done?
- See what you've done!

1060
01:19:19,507 --> 01:19:21,033
Yesterday was brother
Raju's wedding night.

1061
01:19:21,232 --> 01:19:24,682
Still he was sleeping at the back
of the house. Why? Answer me!

1062
01:19:25,297 --> 01:19:28,577
If you didn't consider him
worthy, why did you marry him?

1063
01:19:28,734 --> 01:19:30,783
Who says I don't consider
him worthy of me?

1064
01:19:31,850 --> 01:19:34,266
The truth is I'm not worthy of him.

1065
01:19:36,485 --> 01:19:38,750
Then whatever I had heard...

1066
01:19:38,775 --> 01:19:39,813
All that was a lie.

1067
01:19:41,787 --> 01:19:42,781
You don't know.

1068
01:19:43,482 --> 01:19:45,496
The elders of this house
want to separate us...

1069
01:19:45,834 --> 01:19:47,639
...for their own selfish reasons!

1070
01:19:47,937 --> 01:19:49,375
They want to break our marriage.

1071
01:19:50,475 --> 01:19:53,758
But I'll never let them
fulfill their desire.

1072
01:19:54,775 --> 01:19:57,827
Just think. He protected me...

1073
01:19:58,244 --> 01:20:00,517
...and saved me from defamation.

1074
01:20:01,385 --> 01:20:02,813
Won't I respect him?

1075
01:20:04,938 --> 01:20:08,613
You don't know, Pandu,
he dwells in my heart.

1076
01:20:10,210 --> 01:20:13,383
Forgive me, sister-in-law,
I misunderstood you.

1077
01:20:14,514 --> 01:20:18,000
- You can hit me with your sandals.
- What are you doing?

1078
01:20:18,025 --> 01:20:20,304
Pandu, quickly bring the food!

1079
01:20:20,745 --> 01:20:23,025
- I'm dying of hunger!
- Die!

1080
01:20:23,934 --> 01:20:24,794
Coming!

1081
01:20:25,997 --> 01:20:27,055
What a big glutton they are!

1082
01:20:27,082 --> 01:20:28,681
They're never content no
matter how much you feed them.

1083
01:20:28,854 --> 01:20:31,174
Champa, first go and feed father.

1084
01:20:31,237 --> 01:20:33,472
- Then we'll feed these animals.
- Okay.

1085
01:20:36,107 --> 01:20:37,008
What is this?

1086
01:20:37,604 --> 01:20:39,126
Father is fed this food.

1087
01:20:39,643 --> 01:20:42,000
What can I do, sister-in-law?
I feel sad too.

1088
01:20:42,788 --> 01:20:44,865
- But those...
- Don't worry about them.

1089
01:20:46,271 --> 01:20:48,704
From today I'll take food for father.

1090
01:20:58,963 --> 01:20:59,631
Father.

1091
01:21:06,893 --> 01:21:08,861
- Daughter-in-law, you!
- Yes.

1092
01:21:09,844 --> 01:21:13,354
The family members eat and the
head of the family stays hungry.

1093
01:21:14,057 --> 01:21:15,119
It doesn't look nice.

1094
01:21:16,199 --> 01:21:16,830
Come.

1095
01:21:21,494 --> 01:21:23,336
Today I'll feed you.

1096
01:21:24,469 --> 01:21:25,173
Sit.

1097
01:21:39,100 --> 01:21:41,770
Father, you're crying.

1098
01:21:44,212 --> 01:21:47,532
For the past 20 years I
was craving for this love.

1099
01:21:49,597 --> 01:21:51,902
I was hungry for someone's affection.

1100
01:21:53,662 --> 01:21:54,999
Can I ask you something?

1101
01:21:55,977 --> 01:21:58,293
Why is this injustice going on
in this house for so many years?

1102
01:21:58,364 --> 01:21:59,665
Why doesn't anyone stop it?

1103
01:21:59,852 --> 01:22:01,877
I tried to stop her alone.

1104
01:22:03,811 --> 01:22:08,356
But along with her brother my
wife proved me to be insane...

1105
01:22:09,561 --> 01:22:11,558
...and left me in this hell to die.

1106
01:22:16,244 --> 01:22:18,246
I wanted to bring a mother for Raju.

1107
01:22:19,597 --> 01:22:21,137
But I brought a vamp.

1108
01:22:22,415 --> 01:22:25,562
She didn't let my Raju study.
She kept him as an illiterate.

1109
01:22:25,819 --> 01:22:27,450
So that she can take advantage of it!

1110
01:22:29,478 --> 01:22:33,121
My Raju considers that witch a Goddess!
He worships her!

1111
01:22:34,866 --> 01:22:38,168
Before she kills my Raju, save my son.

1112
01:22:39,174 --> 01:22:40,409
Save my Raju.

1113
01:22:47,793 --> 01:22:50,403
Gauri, Rani work carefully.

1114
01:22:50,428 --> 01:22:52,926
- Sir, where should I keep this?
- On my head.

1115
01:22:53,231 --> 01:22:56,277
Look, if the crop this year is not...

1116
01:23:00,676 --> 01:23:01,903
What are you doing?

1117
01:23:01,928 --> 01:23:03,887
You fool! Did I ask you
to keep it on my head?

1118
01:23:03,912 --> 01:23:06,288
- You said it.
- Keep it there! Go!

1119
01:23:08,179 --> 01:23:10,840
What is it, brother Raju?
You're looking very sad.

1120
01:23:10,913 --> 01:23:12,887
Seems like he didn't
sleep the entire night.

1121
01:23:12,912 --> 01:23:15,223
Stop blabbering and work.

1122
01:23:15,292 --> 01:23:17,011
- We're working.
- [BIRD CHIRPING]

1123
01:23:17,045 --> 01:23:20,644
Oh God! Brother Raju,
here comes your bride.

1124
01:23:24,401 --> 01:23:27,269
Brother Raju, what spell have
you cast on her in one night...

1125
01:23:27,294 --> 01:23:29,454
...that she doesn't even
leave you during the day?

1126
01:23:31,997 --> 01:23:33,060
Why have you come here?

1127
01:23:33,377 --> 01:23:34,769
I want to talk to you.

1128
01:23:36,397 --> 01:23:38,988
Whatever you want to say,
say it in that hut. Come.

1129
01:23:42,072 --> 01:23:43,450
He's taking her in the hut.

1130
01:23:47,548 --> 01:23:51,893
- Listen, I want to tell you...
- I know what you want to say.

1131
01:23:52,214 --> 01:23:54,051
You want to say I'm not worthy of you.

1132
01:23:54,220 --> 01:23:57,540
- Listen to me.
- I've heard it. You said at the fair...

1133
01:23:57,941 --> 01:23:59,901
...you'll marry only a prince...

1134
01:23:59,988 --> 01:24:01,748
- ...not a fool like me.
- But...

1135
01:24:01,938 --> 01:24:04,058
Saru, I'm your husband.

1136
01:24:04,356 --> 01:24:06,365
But I never tried to
assert my right on you.

1137
01:24:07,268 --> 01:24:08,277
Why didn't you?

1138
01:24:08,321 --> 01:24:10,026
What are you doing?

1139
01:24:10,477 --> 01:24:12,238
Marriage is the union of two souls.

1140
01:24:12,867 --> 01:24:14,738
Then let this union take place today.

1141
01:24:15,137 --> 01:24:16,385
[BIRD CHIRPING]

1142
01:24:16,880 --> 01:24:19,332
Do you think that you will
melt me by behaving like this?

1143
01:24:19,926 --> 01:24:23,191
I will die but will not
let you come close to me.

1144
01:24:23,398 --> 01:24:26,058
- Please agree, my prince.
- Never.

1145
01:24:26,858 --> 01:24:30,809
Listen. Don't force me to be 'Meneka'
(Indian mythological danseuse).

1146
01:24:31,160 --> 01:24:33,238
Listen. I am not sage 'Vishwamitra'
(Indian mythological sage)...

1147
01:24:33,263 --> 01:24:35,961
...that I will get lured.

1148
01:24:39,539 --> 01:24:43,020
- Is it? Is that what you think?
- Yes.

1149
01:24:43,760 --> 01:24:44,727
Yes, that is it.

1150
01:24:45,420 --> 01:24:49,941
Do you think that if you do all
this something will happen to me?

1151
01:24:54,128 --> 01:24:56,401
- Can you feel anything?
- No.

1152
01:25:05,550 --> 01:25:07,326
How about now?

1153
01:25:08,142 --> 01:25:09,234
No...

1154
01:25:12,229 --> 01:25:14,545
- What now?
- Yes, I can.

1155
01:25:17,154 --> 01:25:19,778
- Now?
- Yes, I can.

1156
01:25:22,191 --> 01:25:26,069
- Can you feel now?
- Yes, I can.

1157
01:25:53,785 --> 01:25:56,262
- Gauri. Hey, Gauri.
- What is it?

1158
01:25:57,066 --> 01:25:58,668
- I am going home.
- Why?

1159
01:25:59,099 --> 01:26:01,128
I am missing him.

1160
01:26:01,605 --> 01:26:02,628
Hey, listen.

1161
01:27:05,787 --> 01:27:12,418
"Tell us, what did you say
sneakily to your beloved?"

1162
01:27:13,399 --> 01:27:20,262
"Tell us, what did you say
sneakily to your beloved?"

1163
01:27:20,381 --> 01:27:24,919
"My eyes will lower with shyness."

1164
01:27:25,429 --> 01:27:30,069
"I'll feel coy."

1165
01:27:30,460 --> 01:27:32,977
"My eyes will lower with shyness."

1166
01:27:33,051 --> 01:27:35,465
"I'll feel coy."

1167
01:27:35,490 --> 01:27:40,437
"How can I just say
what happened with me?"

1168
01:27:40,475 --> 01:27:43,645
"Ask me, friend."

1169
01:27:43,677 --> 01:27:50,794
"Tell us, what did you say
sneakily to your beloved?"

1170
01:28:21,625 --> 01:28:26,065
"You're under our oath,
don't hide anything from us."

1171
01:28:26,750 --> 01:28:30,915
"Tell me, how did your
garland become a mess?"

1172
01:28:31,065 --> 01:28:33,114
"Tell us!"

1173
01:28:33,667 --> 01:28:35,889
'Tell us!'

1174
01:28:36,451 --> 01:28:41,432
"There was a bee in my garland."

1175
01:28:41,457 --> 01:28:46,338
"I was shooing it away with my hands."

1176
01:28:46,481 --> 01:28:49,801
"It was delicate."

1177
01:28:51,511 --> 01:28:56,615
"It was delicate.
It broke as soon as I touched it."

1178
01:28:56,686 --> 01:29:02,615
"And the flowers got scattered."

1179
01:29:09,930 --> 01:29:17,091
"Tell us, what did you say
sneakily to your beloved?"

1180
01:29:17,594 --> 01:29:24,896
"Tell us, what did you say
sneakily to your beloved?"

1181
01:29:27,673 --> 01:29:32,130
"Tell me, why there are
teeth marks on your lips..."

1182
01:29:32,664 --> 01:29:36,873
"How did you get nail marks here?"

1183
01:29:36,944 --> 01:29:38,984
"Tell us!"

1184
01:29:39,491 --> 01:29:41,911
"Tell us!"

1185
01:29:42,027 --> 01:29:46,920
"I saw a parrot in the night."

1186
01:29:47,125 --> 01:29:52,136
"I was enticed seeing it."

1187
01:29:52,186 --> 01:29:57,690
"I went to pet the lovely parrot."

1188
01:29:59,671 --> 01:30:04,675
"I went to pet the lovely parrot."

1189
01:30:04,711 --> 01:30:10,498
"He pecked on my lips and flew away."

1190
01:30:17,865 --> 01:30:25,034
"Tell us, what did you say
sneakily to your beloved?"

1191
01:30:25,573 --> 01:30:32,753
"Tell us, what did you say
sneakily to your beloved?"

1192
01:30:35,649 --> 01:30:39,950
"Why are your tresses entangled?"

1193
01:30:40,649 --> 01:30:44,771
"Why are you clothes so wrinkled?"

1194
01:30:44,835 --> 01:30:46,835
"Tell us!"

1195
01:30:47,426 --> 01:30:49,756
"Tell us!"

1196
01:30:50,122 --> 01:30:55,002
"There was an unknown pain in my heart."

1197
01:30:55,052 --> 01:30:59,797
"My restlessness grew,
I started suffering."

1198
01:30:59,968 --> 01:31:04,920
"When I couldn't tolerate
the pain anymore..."

1199
01:31:04,992 --> 01:31:11,032
"...I held my heart with my own hands."

1200
01:31:32,565 --> 01:31:36,888
"We can't understand this problem?"

1201
01:31:37,555 --> 01:31:41,635
"Why have you worn the
skirt the wrong way?"

1202
01:31:41,676 --> 01:31:43,676
"Tell us!"

1203
01:31:44,173 --> 01:31:46,274
"Tell us!"

1204
01:31:52,647 --> 01:31:54,764
"You've been caught!"

1205
01:31:54,804 --> 01:31:57,336
"You've been caught!"

1206
01:31:57,670 --> 01:31:59,538
"You've been caught!"

1207
01:31:59,649 --> 01:32:02,703
"Look, she has been caught!"

1208
01:32:07,216 --> 01:32:10,297
"Come here."

1209
01:32:12,172 --> 01:32:15,282
"I'll tell you everything."

1210
01:32:17,137 --> 01:32:19,602
"Come here."

1211
01:32:19,666 --> 01:32:22,057
"I'll tell you everything."

1212
01:32:22,090 --> 01:32:26,890
"I'll not keep any secret from you."

1213
01:32:27,064 --> 01:32:32,578
"What do love-birds say to each other?"

1214
01:32:34,446 --> 01:32:39,991
"What the lamp does with the wick."

1215
01:32:41,825 --> 01:32:48,286
"What the Earth sings to the sky."

1216
01:32:49,282 --> 01:32:54,435
"What the bee tells the bud."

1217
01:32:56,602 --> 01:33:03,450
"Even we said that to each other..."

1218
01:33:03,936 --> 01:33:06,078
"Listen, friend."

1219
01:33:06,291 --> 01:33:08,691
"Listen, friend."

1220
01:33:31,467 --> 01:33:32,263
Mother!

1221
01:33:32,955 --> 01:33:34,355
- Mother!
- What is it, son?

1222
01:33:34,571 --> 01:33:37,331
Look, Ramesh has become a doctor...

1223
01:33:37,402 --> 01:33:39,357
- ...and brought so many degrees.
- Really?

1224
01:33:39,548 --> 01:33:40,668
- Mother.
- Bless you.

1225
01:33:40,693 --> 01:33:42,173
Now your dreams are fulfilled.
Right, Mother?

1226
01:33:42,401 --> 01:33:43,961
- You're happy?
- Yes, son.

1227
01:33:44,387 --> 01:33:47,261
I'm very happy that Ramesh
has become a doctor.

1228
01:33:47,291 --> 01:33:49,171
Ramesh has finished his education.

1229
01:33:49,459 --> 01:33:51,899
Now find a nice girl and get him married.

1230
01:33:52,442 --> 01:33:55,831
So Ramesh, shall we look for
a girl or do you like someone?

1231
01:33:56,611 --> 01:33:58,930
Mother, that...

1232
01:33:58,987 --> 01:34:02,507
What? Tell me who that girl is?
How is her family?

1233
01:34:02,540 --> 01:34:04,260
What does she do? What is her name?

1234
01:34:04,317 --> 01:34:06,850
Brother, her name is Kunika.
She's from a very rich family.

1235
01:34:07,305 --> 01:34:10,644
But there is only one problem.

1236
01:34:10,679 --> 01:34:12,410
What problem?

1237
01:34:13,268 --> 01:34:15,468
She's a modern girl.

1238
01:34:15,850 --> 01:34:19,690
She wants a court marriage,
not the traditional kind.

1239
01:34:19,731 --> 01:34:22,094
We don't care about that.

1240
01:34:22,235 --> 01:34:23,786
We only want a daughter-in-law. Right?

1241
01:34:23,811 --> 01:34:26,211
- Raju is right, son.
- You got mother's permission too.

1242
01:34:26,313 --> 01:34:28,257
Now arrange to bring daughter-in-law.

1243
01:34:34,520 --> 01:34:35,640
Come.

1244
01:34:35,882 --> 01:34:37,167
What is all this commotion?

1245
01:34:37,211 --> 01:34:38,248
It's not a commotion.

1246
01:34:38,296 --> 01:34:40,246
We're bursting crackers for your arrival.

1247
01:34:40,271 --> 01:34:41,500
Shut up, you bloody servant.

1248
01:34:41,611 --> 01:34:45,193
Ramesh, you've brought daughter-in-law!

1249
01:34:46,291 --> 01:34:47,207
- Champa!
- Yes.

1250
01:34:47,247 --> 01:34:50,122
- Champa, quickly bring the lamp.
- There is no need for all that.

1251
01:34:50,195 --> 01:34:52,555
All this is old tradition.
I don't believe in it.

1252
01:34:52,861 --> 01:34:55,746
I just want to take a cold water bath.

1253
01:34:55,795 --> 01:34:57,169
Come on, darling, let us go in.

1254
01:34:57,250 --> 01:34:59,010
Yes, daughter-in-law. Come.

1255
01:35:00,363 --> 01:35:02,637
[BIRD CHIRPING]

1256
01:35:02,802 --> 01:35:05,738
- She's a modern girl.
- Yes.

1257
01:35:05,983 --> 01:35:08,743
Oh God! Such a long journey!

1258
01:35:09,546 --> 01:35:12,324
My entire body is aching!

1259
01:35:15,576 --> 01:35:17,019
If you're tired,
shall I massage your legs?

1260
01:35:17,108 --> 01:35:19,615
- If you don't mind?
- Of course not.

1261
01:35:23,178 --> 01:35:24,365
Brother Ramesh, tea!

1262
01:35:28,132 --> 01:35:31,571
I didn't see anything!

1263
01:35:31,711 --> 01:35:35,019
What an era! It has been 40
years since independence...

1264
01:35:35,189 --> 01:35:38,592
...but still the husbands of our
country are their wife's slaves.

1265
01:35:39,014 --> 01:35:41,553
- Right, Ramesh?
- Stop this nonsense and serve the tea.

1266
01:35:41,785 --> 01:35:43,513
Here. I was about to do that.

1267
01:35:43,676 --> 01:35:44,727
- Tea.
- Have it.

1268
01:35:47,389 --> 01:35:48,819
- What happened, madam?
- What happened?

1269
01:35:48,852 --> 01:35:50,131
What disgusting tea.

1270
01:35:50,211 --> 01:35:51,851
What are you saying, madam?

1271
01:35:51,917 --> 01:35:55,069
People come from far to
drink the tea prepared by me.

1272
01:35:55,140 --> 01:35:56,460
And you're calling it disgusting.

1273
01:35:56,555 --> 01:35:58,675
I think something is wrong
with your taste buds.

1274
01:35:58,947 --> 01:36:02,472
Your husband is a doctor.
Ask him to check you up.

1275
01:36:02,497 --> 01:36:04,662
- Crazy servant!
- She's calling you.

1276
01:36:04,723 --> 01:36:06,857
I'm telling you...

1277
01:36:08,773 --> 01:36:12,253
Look, madam! My name isn't 'servant'!

1278
01:36:12,913 --> 01:36:18,292
My name is Pandu Dhondu Bhikajirao!

1279
01:36:18,332 --> 01:36:20,450
You argue with us, donkey?!

1280
01:36:21,487 --> 01:36:24,592
What an era! You're kicking
me and calling me donkey.

1281
01:36:24,642 --> 01:36:25,693
- Why you...
- Ramesh!

1282
01:36:26,663 --> 01:36:27,691
Pandu, what is all this?

1283
01:36:27,758 --> 01:36:29,398
Just see sister-in-law, this servant...

1284
01:36:29,478 --> 01:36:31,451
- My name isn't servant, my name is...
- Pandu!

1285
01:36:31,531 --> 01:36:32,557
That's right.

1286
01:36:32,598 --> 01:36:35,105
