Do your work.

1287
01:36:36,357 --> 01:36:38,597
Kunika, did you take father's blessings?

1288
01:36:38,622 --> 01:36:40,982
No, I can't go to that madman's room.

1289
01:36:41,117 --> 01:36:43,095
