He's a crazy madman.

1293
01:36:51,213 --> 01:36:54,924
- Do you know what you're saying?
- Sister-in-law, she's right.

1294
01:36:56,469 --> 01:36:57,316
Ramesh!

1295
01:37:02,870 --> 01:37:04,412
