1312
01:38:52,469 --> 01:38:53,773
[GIBBERISH]

1313
01:38:53,836 --> 01:38:56,156
Darn mad goat, talking nonsense!

1314
01:38:57,596 --> 01:39:00,484
Look, madam,
even I know how to abuse in English!

1315
01:39:00,655 --> 01:39:03,956
