1329
01:39:46,343 --> 01:39:47,491
You got defamed yourself.

1330
01:39:47,516 --> 01:39:48,944
- Shut up, you servant!
- Yes, madam!

1331
01:39:50,579 --> 01:39:51,531
- Run!
- You!

1332
01:40:06,889 --> 01:40:11,012
You didn't do the right thing
by bringing him out of the room!

1333
01:40:11,883 --> 01:40:13,990
I know what's right and what's wrong.

1334
01:40:15,077 --> 01:40:16,197
