1336
01:40:21,345 --> 01:40:24,622
Yes, when the elders
of the house forget...

1337
01:40:25,003 --> 01:40:26,683
...the difference between
right and wrong...

1338
01:40:27,231 --> 01:40:29,940
...it's the duty of the juniors
to show them the right way.

1339
01:40:29,965 --> 01:40:31,280
- Daughter-in-law!
- Don't shout!

1340
01:40:32,976 --> 01:40:34,406
Husband is considered God!

1341
01:40:34,852 --> 01:40:38,072
But you treated your
husband worse than animals!

1342
01:40:38,566 --> 01:40:41,429
You aren't even worthy
of being called a human!

1343
01:40:41,932 --> 01:40:43,487
We're animals!

1344
01:40:43,512 --> 01:40:45,312
Why didn't I go deaf before hearing that?

1345
01:40:45,458 --> 01:40:49,232
Thank God that my son Raju didn't hear...

1346
01:40:49,826 --> 01:40:51,758
...whatever you said.

1347
01:40:51,799 --> 01:40:53,189
