1360
01:41:31,257 --> 01:41:33,607
- You called my mother a witch!
- Raju.

1361
01:41:33,635 --> 01:41:34,904
- Move away!
- Leave her!

1362
01:41:34,929 --> 01:41:37,396
- She called you a witch.
- You're under my oath! Leave her!

1363
01:41:43,221 --> 01:41:45,919
Did you see the greatness of my mother?

1364
01:41:47,054 --> 01:41:50,721
You abused her so much, but she saved you!

1365
01:41:51,019 --> 01:41:52,748
