previous months there were fires in...

1458
01:50:41,432 --> 01:50:44,790
...the fields and well
and the pumps were burnt.

1459
01:50:44,851 --> 01:50:47,087
- But there's a fire this month too...
- Quiet.

1460
01:50:48,423 --> 01:50:52,328
Quickly. Put it in.

1461
01:51:03,450 --> 01:51:05,387
- Ramlal, water the garden properly.
- Start. [BIRD CHIRPING]

1462
01:51:05,552 --> 01:51:10,033
Pandu, my husband toils day and night!
And you don't care at all.

1463
01:51:10,166 --> 01:51:12,703
There has been so much loss? Useless!

1464
01:51:12,792 --> 01:51:15,001
Saru, what are you doing?

1465
01:51:15,547 --> 01:51:18,147
Pandu is our old servant
and you're slapping him.

1466
01:51:18,346 --> 01:51:19,813
Then ask him...

1467
01:51:20,274 --> 01:51:22,336
...why was there a fire in the
storehouse, the fields and the well.

1468
01:51:22,478 --> 01:51:24,336
Fire! Forget the storehouse and fields...

1469
01:51:24,361 --> 01:51:27,047
...in the last two years there wasn't
any fire in the entire village, Saru.

1470
01:51:27,150 --> 01:51:29,469
I'm not saying it.
It's written in the accounts books.

1471
01:51:29,683 --> 01:51:32,828
It's written there has been a loss of
millions of rupees due to the fire.

1472
01:51:33,385 --> 01:51:34,632
Loss of millions of rupees!

1473
01:51:35,144 --> 01:51:36,875
- Who writes the accounts book?
- Accountant!

1474
01:51:37,471 --> 01:51:41,977
Accountant, how is this week for me?
Tell me.

1475
01:51:42,027 --> 01:51:45,508
Your misfortune is going to start!

1476
01:51:45,611 --> 01:51:46,865
- Accountant!
- Yes!

1477
01:51:47,578 --> 01:51:48,320
Yes, sir!

1478
01:51:49,962 --> 01:51:52,047
What's written in this accounts book?
Read it out.

1479
01:51:52,623 --> 01:51:55,328
- The storehouse of the grains...
- Why are you looking around?

1480
01:51:55,386 --> 01:51:57,557
Read properly what's written in it!
Read it quickly.

1481
01:51:57,688 --> 01:52:00,768
Due to a fire in the
food grain storehouse...

1482
01:52:00,898 --> 01:52:02,968
...there was a loss of Rs. 200,000.

1483
01:52:02,977 --> 01:52:05,132
Seems like your eyesight has become weak.

1484
01:52:05,336 --> 01:52:07,485
It's written that there has
been a profit of Rs.200,000...

1485
01:52:07,510 --> 01:52:08,625
...because of the sales.

1486
01:52:08,681 --> 01:52:10,873
And you're saying there was a loss!
Betrayer!

1487
01:52:10,898 --> 01:52:14,312
Uncle, there is no need to act too smart!

1488
01:52:14,651 --> 01:52:17,026
My wife is educated.
She told me everything!

1489
01:52:17,411 --> 01:52:20,680
Accountant, tell me clearly!
Was there a fire in the storage house?

1490
01:52:20,868 --> 01:52:23,594
That... there... it...

1491
01:52:23,795 --> 01:52:24,915
You won't tell me like that!

1492
01:52:25,124 --> 01:52:27,324
Pandu! Where is my whip?

1493
01:52:27,357 --> 01:52:29,633
The whip will be of no use in this matter!

1494
01:52:29,859 --> 01:52:32,396
Here is the gun.
There are real bullets in it.

1495
01:52:32,611 --> 01:52:34,451
One shot and the truth will come out.

1496
01:52:34,675 --> 01:52:35,352
Shoot him!

1497
01:52:36,201 --> 01:52:38,561
