Mother! The first word
that a child says...

2067
02:23:14,836 --> 02:23:18,561
...after being born is mother.

2068
02:23:19,438 --> 02:23:21,994
He learns and says a lot
of things while growing up.

2069
02:23:24,397 --> 02:23:27,457
But I didn't learn
anything other than mother.

2070
02:23:27,990 --> 02:23:29,576
I didn't say anything else.

2071
02:23:31,442 --> 02:23:34,616
Tell me, why did you do all this?

2072
02:23:36,905 --> 02:23:38,521
You should've just told me.

2073
