I would've killed myself.

2077
02:23:57,664 --> 02:23:59,256
Then why did you do all this?

2078
02:24:01,311 --> 02:24:02,131
Tell me.

2079
02:24:03,415 --> 02:24:04,717
Why did you do it?

2080
02:24:06,482 --> 02:24:07,123
Mother...

2081
02:24:08,677 --> 02:24:11,877
...your unfortunate son has a last wish.

2082
02:24:12,913 --> 02:24:14,334
Please fulfill it.

2083
02:24:16,624 --> 02:24:18,630
It's forbidden for women
to come to the crematorium.

2084
02:24:19,675 --> 02:24:21,670
But please come for me.

2085
02:24:22,854 --> 02:24:24,458
And before my pyre is set on fire...

2086
02:24:25,906 --> 02:24:30,006
...call me son once from your heart.

2087
02:24:32,254 --> 02:24:33,967
So that I can die peacefully.

2088
02:24:36,095 --> 02:24:39,881
I don't want anything else. Nothing else.

2089
02:24:53,450 --> 02:24:55,458
[COUGHING AND VOMITING]

2090
02:25:11,608 --> 02:25:12,741
Doctor!

2091
02:25:19,235 --> 02:25:20,246
Come quickly!

2092
02:25:21,165 --> 02:25:22,245
Quickly!

2093
02:25:25,943 --> 02:25:26,882
Come.

2094
02:25:34,530 --> 02:25:36,816
All this... -There is no need to be
scared, daughter-in-law.

2095
02:25:36,940 --> 02:25:39,241
We've locked your husband in the room.

2096
02:25:39,314 --> 02:25:40,842
And we have the key to it.

2097
02:25:41,017 --> 02:25:43,057
It's good that you've brought the doctor.

2098
02:25:43,266 --> 02:25:47,193
He's counting his last breath.
But we'll have to save his life.

2099
02:25:47,273 --> 02:25:50,474
But for that you'll have to
bear a small inconvenience.

2100
02:25:50,506 --> 02:25:53,117
You'll have to sign on the will.

2101
02:25:53,158 --> 02:25:57,376
Scoundrels, all your life you
made Raju's life miserable!

2102
02:25:57,688 --> 02:25:59,837
Now you want take
advantage of his death too!

2103
02:26:00,054 --> 02:26:01,944
Even animals aren't so heartless!

2104
02:26:02,755 --> 02:26:06,111
You want wealth? Take it.
Tell me where I have to sign.

2105
02:26:06,190 --> 02:26:07,005
Ramesh!

2106
02:26:26,594 --> 02:26:29,019
You'll not sign on these papers!

2107
02:26:35,228 --> 02:26:36,472
Open the door, daughter-in-law!

2108
02:26:38,336 --> 02:26:40,137
- Have you gone mad, Mother?
- Leave me!

2109
02:26:41,113 --> 02:26:43,385
Thieves have an honour too.

2110
02:26:43,589 --> 02:26:45,222
They're afraid of God.

2111
02:26:45,972 --> 02:26:49,796
But us, we stooped so low...

2112
02:26:50,733 --> 02:26:53,597
...that we were adamant on
killing that innocent Raju...

2113
02:26:54,444 --> 02:27:00,534
...who kept worshipping a
witch like me all his life!

2114
02:27:01,301 --> 02:27:04,275
But today if we save him...

2115
02:27:04,852 --> 02:27:06,986
...maybe we can repent for our sins!

2116
02:27:07,358 --> 02:27:09,433
Maybe the Lord will forgive us.

2117
02:27:10,344 --> 02:27:11,183
But...

2118
02:27:11,886 --> 02:27:16,940
But if he dies today,
it won't be just Raju's murder.

2119
02:27:17,478 --> 02:27:19,165
It'll be the murder of all the mothers!

2120
02:27:19,371 --> 02:27:21,595
It'll be the murder of the word "mother"!

2121
02:27:21,871 --> 02:27:24,932
And I'll be the murderer! A mother!

2122
02:27:24,957 --> 02:27:26,172
What nonsense are you uttering, sister?

2123
02:27:26,643 --> 02:27:29,323
How did you develop
feelings for Raju today?

2124
02:27:29,608 --> 02:27:31,298
We can't lose the wealth for which...

2125
02:27:31,323 --> 02:27:33,300
...we waited for 15 years.

2126
02:27:33,511 --> 02:27:35,775
At least think about your own son!

2127
02:27:37,549 --> 02:27:41,587
Kaykeyi only exiled Ram for
14 years for her Bharat.

2128
02:27:42,860 --> 02:27:47,401
But I sentenced my Raju
to death for my son.

2129
02:27:48,908 --> 02:27:53,440
Ramesh, if you love and respect
your mother even a bit...

2130
02:27:53,817 --> 02:27:55,141
...give me the keys.

2131
02:27:55,524 --> 02:27:58,861
But first give me the property papers.

2132
02:27:58,940 --> 02:28:01,299
Look, son... Saru!

2133
02:28:07,712 --> 02:28:09,876
- Saru, that...
- Give me the property papers, Mother.

2134
02:28:10,061 --> 02:28:10,884
Or else I...

2135
02:28:14,039 --> 02:28:17,470
You behave with your mother in this
way, scoundrel!

2136
02:28:31,962 --> 02:28:33,286
Bravo, son!

2137
02:28:34,649 --> 02:28:35,514
Good!

2138
02:28:37,045 --> 02:28:39,572
You've returned your mother's love nicely.

2139
02:28:40,750 --> 02:28:44,483
But it's not your fault, Ramesh.

2140
02:28:45,136 --> 02:28:48,377
It was the Lord's justice...

2141
02:28:49,207 --> 02:28:52,048
...in the form of this slap.

2142
02:28:53,694 --> 02:28:55,272
You've proved it today...

2143
02:28:56,217 --> 02:29:01,819
...that a serpent can give
birth only to a snake...

2144
02:29:03,153 --> 02:29:05,635
...not a son like my Raju.

2145
02:29:07,152 --> 02:29:08,650
But remember.

2146
02:29:09,511 --> 02:29:13,720
Even if you kill me,
I'll not give you this property papers!

2147
02:29:14,350 --> 02:29:16,108
Mother, better give me these papers...

2148
02:29:16,133 --> 02:29:17,764
...or else I know other means!

2149
02:29:17,804 --> 02:29:20,287
She has gone mad!
Snatch the papers quickly!

2150
02:29:21,130 --> 02:29:23,056
- Give me these papers, Mother!
- I won't.

2151
02:29:26,422 --> 02:29:27,448
You won't.

2152
02:29:30,678 --> 02:29:33,111
Raju!

2153
02:29:35,512 --> 02:29:37,174
Ramesh, quickly snatch the papers!

2154
02:29:39,769 --> 02:29:42,853
Raju! Dear Raju!

2155
02:29:45,788 --> 02:29:47,704
Raju!

2156
02:29:47,752 --> 02:29:48,946
No!

2157
02:29:50,232 --> 02:29:51,046
No!

2158
02:29:53,429 --> 02:29:54,459
Raju!

2159
02:29:57,032 --> 02:29:58,480
Dear Raju!

2160
