[BIRD CHIRPING]

2174
02:32:50,486 --> 02:32:53,513
Father, I'm leaving this house.

2175
02:32:55,216 --> 02:32:57,247
I know it's the duty of a son...

2176
02:32:57,833 --> 02:32:59,775
...to look after his
parents in their old age.

2177
02:33:01,082 --> 02:33:03,134
But maybe it was not in my fate.

2178
02:33:05,594 --> 02:33:08,875
So I've transferred the
property in mother's name.

2179
02:33:11,073 --> 02:33:12,765
Father, take care of my mother.

2180
02:33:13,665 --> 02:33:14,485
Come, Saru.

2181
02:33:27,214 --> 02:33:28,466
Mother, what are you doing?

2182
02:33:30,751 --> 02:33:34,017
I know, son, I'm your culprit.

2183
02:33:34,954 --> 02:33:36,539
Punish me if you want.

2184
02:33:37,432 --> 02:33:41,026
But please don't leave your mother.

2185
02:33:41,589 --> 02:33:45,800
I don't want this property!

2186
02:33:45,825 --> 02:33:47,345
Nothing!

2187
02:33:48,467 --> 02:33:54,478
I want my son, my Raju.

2188
02:33:55,544 --> 02:33:57,223
I want my son.

2189
02:33:58,075 --> 02:33:59,791
I want my son, Raju.

